headline: CME Group’s rating bumped as stock benefits from market volatility
summary: Investing.com -- Raymond James upgraded CME Group Inc (NASDAQ:CME) to "Outperform" from "Market Perform," given the strong trading volumes driven by economic uncertainty and geopolitical tensions. Price target was set at $287 for the exchange operator, as the company is well-positioned to thrive in a volatile market environment.
